Name: jSynthesizer.
Author: Adam Steinberger.
Homepage: http://amsteinberger.wordpress.com/code/jsynthesizer/.
GitHub: https://github.com/asteinberger/jSynthesizer/.
Google Code: http://code.google.com/p/jsynthesizer/.

JSynthesizer is a java synthesizer. Synthesize music using the jSynthesizer Java API for use with the Java Sound API.

To use jSynthesizer in a java project, copy all the files from the jSynthesizer source code directory and paste them into the source code directory of the project you want to use jSynthesizer with.